items.text: Awesome food!!!
The place to go for great traditional zhi char! Check it out!
Milk powder ribs, oatmeal prawns & prawn paste chicken are must tries! Not to mention that the prices are very affordable!
cold cockles come with a tart acidic sauce that masks any fishiness from the cockles. the butter ribs are de-boned for convenience.
Must tries include the Mayo Prawn and famous Butter Pork. Don't bother with the soups - not that great.
Yam lover must order the yam dishes...
Veg with 3 type of eggs, Ngo Hiang, Honey Rib chicken.  Damn shiok
Try Marmite Chicken. It's not on the menu.   : )
Butter ribs, drunken cockles, fuyong egg are their signature dishes which makes us come back for more!
Love their Chilli crab that is value for money .
Best Zi char!! Golden mushroom tofu, milk powder pork rib, black pepper venison!!
Awesome tze char. Butter pork ribs, vege with 3 eggs and hotplate tofu are must-tries!
The cockles MUST-TRY
Herbal chicken soup is great! Tender chicken in rich herbal soup. Yummy!!
glad they are open on 大年初一!!!!
Venison is tasty and really tender! Cockles awesome as always :)
Decent zhichar. The san lao horfun has much wei kee. Parking can be an issue. Very vigilent parking aunties.
Must order this! Yumzxzxz

Burst of flavours! Thumbs up!

Delicious food cum great service.. Fast in serving the food.. Once try, will surely patronize again.. >_<

The butter pork ribs/milk power pork ribs and drunken cockles is their speciality. Service is fast and food good. Most importantly, the price is cheap. Avoid weekends.

Definitely butter porky ribs...
The food is good with the butter pork ribs

Milk powder pork rib, honey chicken, salted egg prawn, mushroom tofu and drunken cockles all lived up to expectation. But, you need to book and you need your whole gang to be here to be seated!
Cold seeham!!
This place is crazy!!! 530pm and the crowd is forming already!!!
Almost everything here is good, except the Black Pepper Crab and a few others that does not have enough flavour .
Try the Cold Cockles  - If you like raw cockles, this is a refreshing change literally. #cockles #garlic
Does not accept reservation but seating is fast when all diners are present. Service is fast and value for $$$!
will be back for more affordable and delicious zi char! can't go wrong with their milk powder chicken.
Try the Chicken In Salted Egg Yolk
Milk powder pork ribs, herbal chicken, golden mushroom tofu and 3 eggs veg

Try the Chilli Crab

Yummy butter pork chops!
Get your family and relatives to come together at the same time. They will give you the seats once all your guests arrive.
Try the garlic seaham also! Its famous!!

Their specialties here live up to their name. Try the drunken cold cockles, spinach trio eggs and milk powder pork ribs. You'll definitely like it.
It's better to make a reservation otherwise may need to wait at least 30 min for a table
Will be under renovation from 19 May to mid June
Try the butter (milk powder) pork ribs and golden mushrooms. Yummy!
You can ask for Cereal Prawns without shells!
The butter ribs. I call it The Heroin Ribs cos I'm always back for more.
BUTTER PORK RIBS! and the cockles! must-trys!

Butter pork ribs

must try the garlic sea ham.. gd.

like the by the road setting, low housing nearby... plus the light breeze n evening sun

for adventure ones..... butter milk pork ribs

Three types of eggs
